{
  "title": "Fragrant Malty Syrian Cassaba Stew",
  "description": "A tender and malty Syrian dish featuring cassaba, cooked to perfection in a wok, this stew is a quick fix for a delicious meal. It is shojin-friendly and slow-cooked to bring out the flavors.",
